<TD BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" ALIGN="CENTER" VALIGN="MIDDLE">
<table><tr><td align=center><a href="http://www.worldofspectrum.org/infoseekid.cgi?id=0005187" target="wos"><IMG WIDTH=80 HEIGHT=30 SRC="bigwos.gif" alt="Search WOS" BORDER=0></a></td></tr>
